      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKETS PLEASE (8) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Was too tough when scoring last time over 388m at this track in a NG (21.91). Has a good record here at this journey including three wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. FEDERAL ICEMAN (2) boasts a strong record this journey with nine wins and two minors from 15 tries. Was out of placings last time (22.42) at this track in a NG, finishing fifth and beaten 7 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. LAURIE'S RUPEE (1) has a strong record this journey here with four wins and a minor from seven starts. In the money last time at The Gardens (23.19) in a Free For All, finishing a 7 length third. Looks well placed here and among the chances. MY MACHINE (7) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
